@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
actor Pilot as Pil
participant "Drohne (Kamera)" as K
participant "Prozessor" as P
participant "KI-Modell (Ring)" as A
participant "Flugsteuerung" as S
participant "Ground Station" as G

K->P: Live-Stream Frame
activate P

' Pfad für die Ringerkennung
P->A: Bilddaten zur Inferenz
activate A
alt Ring erkannt
    A->S: Koordinaten (X, Y)
    activate S
    S->S: PID-Flugkorrektur
    S->S: Motoren anpassen
    deactivate S
else Kein Ring
    A->S: Status: "Suche"
end
deactivate A

' Pfad für den Videostream zur Ground Station
P->G: Videodaten senden (RTP/UDP)
activate G
G->Pil: Video anzeigen
deactivate G

deactivate P
@enduml